                <p>Vehicles first used before 1&nbsp;April&nbsp;1986 don’t need to have hazard warning devices.</p>
                <p>Vehicles first used on or after 1&nbsp;April&nbsp;1986 must be fitted with an amber side repeater indicator on each side.
